I      V. OS Functions and Development Notes
Navigation: Ensure all app navigation buttons are functional.
Web Integration: Ensure the web browser application is fully functional.
Interactivity: Ensure all OS and app buttons are enabled and fully functional.
Design: Develop distinct, high-quality designs for each application.
App Sections: Each application must include the following dedicated sections:
{App-Name} (Main View)
Community
Help
Feedback & Suggestions
Window Behavior: App windows must support close, open, minimize, and maximize functionality, correctly fitting the screen to the taskbar.
AI Development Note: Add a sub-description note to AI (New instruction for the development process).
